### Tải extension REST Client rồi ấn send request nó sẽ trả ra response cho mình

### GET all products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products
Accept: application/json

###

### GET product by ID - tìm sản phẩm tồn tại
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Accept: application/json

###

### GET product by ID - id không tồn tại (expect 500)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/9999
Accept: application/json

###

### GET search products - keyword hợp lệ
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=áo
Accept: application/json

###

### GET search products - keyword tiếng Anh
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=shirt
Accept: application/json

###

### GET search products - keyword không có kết quả
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=xyzkhongtontai
Accept: application/json

###

### GET search products - keyword rỗng (trả về tất cả)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=
Accept: application/json
